    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4–12</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The U tile is often considered difficult to use (especially without Q), but -URE gives it a productive home. Combined with the common R and E tiles, -URE converts awkward U-heavy racks into legitimate scoring plays and bingo candidates.</p>

